Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He out-negatived the Negative Ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... When it comes to thinking negatively...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll have you know I'm unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He's super confident in a bad way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime is over, Special Zombie Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop him down from the legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Oars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blazing Knight Sanji!!\NKick Down the Fake Wedding!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you managed to throttle or kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would simply mean the zombies\Nwould no longer be my servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't bring your shadow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. My ability allows me\Nto reign over shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you'll have to do\Nto realize your dream:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make the person currently\Nreigning over the shadows--me--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,order the shadows to return to their masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll return to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Isn't it simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd need to hurt me badly enough\Nthat I'd be willing to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But considering your level of strength,\Nyou couldn't even lay a hand on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to defeat my clone, Doppelman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I was brimming with\Noverconfidence and arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't take long for me to learn how\Nimportant it is to have good subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man who will become the\NKing of the Pirates without lifting a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use the strength of others to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who will\Nbecome King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your zombie said the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can imagine, when its new\Nbody is nothing like the original,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the shadow retains even more\Nof its original master's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't last forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, it will forget\Neverything pertaining to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will become a zombie\Nthat is completely loyal to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong a zombie's will might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will ultimately serve me unconditionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting it back in just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's blocking all of my punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rowdy brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick his butt! Trample him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But watch out for his salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I'm the only one who can\Nstand up to the Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was supposed to be\Nmy time to shine, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the other pirates quickly\Nsuccumbed to my Negative Ghosts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mackerel... I'm worse than mackerel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I want a feral dog to step on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for walking on the same earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected one of the men to be immune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all right. I'll just have\Nthe Wild Zombies kill Mr. Long Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! I can't use my Salt Stars like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to pull out of this? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You got me! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! We killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Keep your hands over your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be another one of his tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right! He's fumbling\Naround with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to get\Nthe salt in our mouths?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Star! Star! Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pepper Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my chance! Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Negative Nose, you weasel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to tricking people, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup! Drop the cool act!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you in your tracks! Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rottin' hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't move, I'll start with--hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nuts! I can't let my guard\Ndown for a second around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to come up with a way\Nto defeat Negative Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bear zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that stuffed animal\Nwas so nimble and powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here he can't even reach\Nthe zipper on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if I upset you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:12:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I wanna go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Stay back, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Don't follow me, bear!\NI said to stay back, bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep back, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! Stay away, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to lose!\NWait, wait, wait! You little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd you go?\NHuh? Are you over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep back, Mr. Negative Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come after me, bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! I'm starting to get really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip! Skip! Skip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your grubby hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:15:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting,\NNami-san. Your knight is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake! Shake your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four!\NOne, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I feel like I haven't gone\Nswimming in ages. I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I sink like a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:16:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho-hoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rather rash of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you had swallowed the salt water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could handle a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you drank a lot,\Nthe salt would purify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! You can be such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, you're in safe hands--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My word! Is she a goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. It's Nami-san. It really is Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her beauty can be deceptive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I thought I recued\Na goddess by mistake. Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was so surprised.\NBut this is definitely Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I thought I accidentally rescued a fairy\Nby mistake. You're a deceptive little kitten.\N--Sheesh! What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you're part of the crew\Nthat was on that pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-An angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, she's human. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she had me scared there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you! I really don't blame you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san and rice are about the only\Nthings that look this good in white!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must she look so stinking good in white?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are they going on about?\N--It throws me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lowly pirate! I don't need\Nto be chums with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly hit Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a lady is in the vicinity,\Nyou should avoid attacks that could hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you dodged that, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've already lost your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, one of our new zombies\Nwas oddly obsessed with that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He retained some will of his own,\Nso he wasn't fully subservient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pursue that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that was your zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that your shadow\Nwasn't put into a General Zombie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your fighting ability\Ncan't be all that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, that penguin talked big,\Nbut was terribly weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm known as one of the Phantoms\Nand lead the General Zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was impudent of that small fry to defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A heavenly maiden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was a heavenly maiden. Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely Nami-san. No mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure what I'd do\Nif she was a divine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't heave a sigh of relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it doesn't matter how\Nobsessed you are with that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to marry her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take a word of advice\Nand leave that woman with me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you spend the rest of\Nyour life hiding in the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rather busy at the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your captain's zombie may have crushed\Nsome of my most powerful subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I deal with that, I need to kiss my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you understand.\NI'm in a foul mood right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to deal with weaklings like--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Fur Face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He weighs 300kg!\NHow did that man send him flying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the "invisible man"\NUsopp mentioned, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that kick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sent me flying even though\NHogback has transplanted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the power of wild animals into my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Could he\Ntell what I was about to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basses Côte!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the beast that showed up on Sunny\Nand licked Robin-chan, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has caught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you ogled at Nami-san's\Nbare skin in the bath, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be my blushing bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tendron! Flanchet! Quasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so strong?! This is their small fry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queue! Cuisseau! Jarret!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:22:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she unconscious?! You didn't\Nget rough with her, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Marriage," my ass!\NTake a good look at my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you under my feet\Nand turn you into croquette!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'll have to retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got Usopp's salt balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? It's salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veau Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insane! This guy doesn't even have a bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you were in a foul mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't begin to describe mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad I feel like my body could explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:23:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And unfortunately for you, there is bad\Nblood between us over one other thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have some bad blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You... You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just met you for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole one of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Clear-Clear History? Sanji's Stolen Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
